OL,3,CAround 300 SEN children in NI waiting
OL,4,Cfor school place
OL,6,FThe Education Authority (EA) has
OL,7,Fapologised to almost 300 families with
OL,8,Fchildren who have special educational
OL,9,Fstatements and are still waiting for
OL,10,Fconfirmation of a school placement.
OL,12,FIn an interview with UTV, the
OL,13,Feducation body said work to provide
OL,14,Ffamilies will continue over the summer
OL,15,Fholidays and that the number of
OL,16,Fchildren still waiting "will be
OL,17,Freduced in the coming weeks".
