OL,3,CAround 300 SEN children in NI waiting
OL,4,Cfor school place
OL,6,FAs of Thursday 27th June, 3,339
OL,7,Fchildren who are at transition periods
OL,8,Fof nursery, primary one and year 8
OL,9,Fhave been placed, while around 270 are
OL,10,Fstill waiting.
OL,12,FOne of those children affected is
OL,13,FAlison McClean's son, Jackson.
OL,15,FHe has a special educational needs
OL,16,Fstatement and is currently at a
OL,17,Fmainstream school where he has a full-
OL,18,Ftime 1-2-1 assistant.
