OL,3,CAround 300 SEN children in NI waiting
OL,4,Cfor school place
OL,6,FHis mum has been advised however that
OL,7,Fhe would benefit from accessing a
OL,8,Fspecialist setting. So far there has
OL,9,Fbeen no update to his application.
OL,11,F"I don't want him to be anxious over
OL,12,Fthe summer break not knowing what
OL,13,Fschool he'll be going to. Even for
OL,14,Fsimple things like knowing what
OL,15,Funiform I should be buying him,"
OL,16,Fexplained Alison.
OL,18,FSt Columban's primary in Kilkeel is a
OL,19,Funique educational setting in Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
