OL,4,Cfor school place
OL,6,FIt opened as a mainstream school in
OL,7,F2018 but subsequently added specialist
OL,8,Ffacilities for children with special
OL,9,Feducational needs.
OL,11,F"In terms of scale of what we did we
OL,12,Fwent form staff of 23/24 we went to 44/
OL,13,F45 overnight," Principal Julian Kelly
OL,14,Ftold UTV.
OL,16,F"A lot of children are non-verbal and
OL,17,Fnot toilet trained so the learning was
OL,18,Fsteep but as a school it's the best
OL,19,Fthing we have ever done.
