OL,6,F"The mainstream children do not see
OL,7,Fany difference with those children,
OL,8,Fthey are part of their school, and
OL,9,Fthey gain as much as the children who
OL,10,Fare in the provision."
OL,12,FFor parents like Andrew Cunningham,
OL,13,Fwho live in Kilkeel, the school has
OL,14,Fbeen a great success for children. His
OL,15,Feldest son is in the mainstream P4
OL,16,Fclass and his youngest son, Shay who
OL,17,Fhas Autism Spectrum Disorder, is in
OL,18,Fthe P2 early years class.
