OL,6,F"I can't express how grateful we are
OL,7,Fto have this facility on our
OL,8,Fdoorstep," he told UTV.
OL,10,F"Shay's development has been very
OL,11,Frapid over the last two years, a big
OL,12,Fthing was his loss of speech at around
OL,13,Fa year and a half, but now he has full
OL,14,Fspeech.
OL,16,F"It's not only the social skills he's
OL,17,Fbeen taught with his friends, but he's
OL,18,Falso up to speed with where he should
OL,19,Fbe in terms of his learning
OL,20,Fdevelopment at six years of age should
OL,21,Fbe."
