OL,6,FElaine Craig is the interim assistant
OL,7,Fdirector of special educational needs
OL,8,Fstatutory services within children and
OL,9,Fyoung peoples' services at the EA.
OL,11,F"The majority of our children who have
OL,12,Fa statement will be in mainstream with
OL,13,Fsupport and others who will be in
OL,14,Fspecialist provision and then others
OL,15,Fin special schools," she told UTV.
