OL,6,F"Over the last number of months 3,339
OL,7,Fchildren who are at transition periods
OL,8,Fof nursery, primary one and year 8 -
OL,9,Fwe still have around 270 yet to place,
OL,10,FI'm sorry we're in that position, I
OL,11,Fwish they were in a position where
OL,12,Fthey were placed and knew now, that
OL,13,Fnumber will reduce in coming weeks."
