OL,6,FWhen asked if all outstanding
OL,7,Fplacements would be issued by the
OL,8,Fstart of the new school term, Ms Craig
OL,9,Fsaid: "It would be wrong of me to be
OL,10,Fabsolutely say for sure - but what I
OL,11,Fwill say is that we will have all of
OL,12,Four children placed within the next
OL,13,Facademic year, and work is ongoing
OL,14,Fover the summer and it will happen to
OL,15,Fensure schools are ready for those
OL,16,Fchildren and to ensure we have
OL,17,Fchildren in place."
